name: Techpunk Mask | Wearable LoRA
description:
NEW V0.5!

full 4 model in Zip.

Two categories

  • a full coverage techpunkmask

  • a full coverage VR - techpunkmask

Subsidiary structure

  • with designed antenna

  • with small antennae

  • with complex electronics

  • with a camera attached to it

  • with a green light on his face

Character distribution

(a lot involved in the training set, you can use negative prompts to exclude)

  • black bangs double ponytail

  • black hair with bangs

Disadvantages

models from 1 to 4:

1. Overfitting

2. Saturation reduction

3. Too many textures

——————————————————————

DESCRIPTION

This LoRA can wear a transitional technological mask for the character. It is suitable for close-up portraits, and it can be used with "Urban Samurai" to get a picture with a strong sense of cyberpunk style.

How to use

<lora:techpunkmask_v0.2:0.8>

Tag:

  • scifi techmask and headphones

Practices

Key prompt:

  • wearing scifi techmask and headphones with complex electronics

  • wearing black techwear jacket and orange trousers with buckle and tape

  • <lora:techpunkmask_v0.2:0.8>

  • <lora:urbansamurai_v0.3:0.5>

MORE

Reach me on Twitter if you wish to contribute to improving this mod, Thx! https://twitter.com/Artist3YeHe
